title: macbbok air 820-3437-B not charging
message: have a macbook air with liquid damaged after cleaned turned on and works fine  but will not charge battery, it detects it but will show as not charging, please help, thanks.

title: macbbok air 820-3437-B not charging
message: Tried known good battery? Tried known good I/O Board and I/O Flex Cable? If so, check resistance between pins 17 and 18 as well as 27 and 28 of the ISL6259.
